    "13 These are important criticisms because they illuminate the underlying techno-philosophical shortcomings of the state-of-the-art.",
    "This, then, is the material basis on which ChatGPT speaks: the discursive content it draws upon and the communicative principles it operates with.",
    "Foucault did not theorise the nonhuman; foot_12 nor did he define the subject-it would have been inimical to his non-essentialist project and his scepticism towards humanist assumptions.",
